<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>... و <span class="c4">[مَفْعُلة]</span>، بضم العين<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[ر]</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[المَقْبُرة]</span>: موضع القبور،<span class="c5"> قال اللّاه تعالى:</span> حَتّاى زُرْتُمُ الْمَقاابِرَ <span class="c2">«٢»</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
